\pard\keepn\nowidctlpar\sb120\sa120\sl240\slmult0\tx360\b\f1\fs24 1.\tab Design\f0\fs20\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\li720\sa120\b0\f1 The component provides the login and logout action support for the Online Review application. Users can pass the user name and password for authentication. In order to make the component as flexible as possible, this component leverages the TopCoder Authenticator Factory framework to make the authentication pluggable. Before integrating the authenticator, application users must implement AuthResponsePaser interface to custom their own \ldblquote login\rdblquote  and \ldblquote logout\rdblquote  function. In the current version, SecurityManagerAuthenticator is implemented to authenticate the user name and password by employing the LoginBean from the Security Manager component.\par
\par
\pard\keepn\nowidctlpar\sb120\sa120\sl240\slmult0\tx0\b 1.1\tab Design Patterns \par
\pard\nowidctlpar\li720\sa120\b0 The LoginActionServlet and LoginActions follow the MVC design pattern of struts.\f0\par
\f1 AuthResponseParser implements the Strategy pattern.\f0\par
